<h3 class="font-outfit text-lg font-bold text-amber-300 mt-6 mb-3">HEAVY FRAME MODELS</h3>
<p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">These wheelchairs have bulky and heavier frames, allowing the chair to lend its weight to your character’s attacks. It also makes them a bigger target.</p>
